---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import placeholder from '/src/img/male-placeholder.jpeg';

<section class="py-10 bg-gray-100 sm:py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-7xl sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-800 sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">¿Qué opinan nuestros clientes?</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 mx-auto mt-8 text-center lg:max-w-full sm:mt-12 lg:mt-20 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-x-6 xl:gap-x-12 gap-y-6">
            <div class="overflow-hidden bg-white rounded-md shadow">
                <div class="px-8 py-12">
                    <div class="relative w-24 h-24 mx-auto">
                        <img class="relative object-cover w-24 h-24 mx-auto rounded-full" src="/src/img/male-placeholder.jpeg" alt="" />
                        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-600 rounded-full w-7 h-7">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                                <path
                                    d="M20.309 17.708C22.196 15.66 22.006 13.03 22 13V5a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-6c-1.103 0-2 .897-2 2v7a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h3.078a2.89 2.89 0 0 1-.429 1.396c-.508.801-1.465 1.348-2.846 1.624l-.803.16V20h1c2.783 0 4.906-.771 6.309-2.292zm-11.007 0C11.19 15.66 10.999 13.03 10.993 13V5a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-6c-1.103 0-2 .897-2 2v7a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h3.078a2.89 2.89 0 0 1-.429 1.396c-.508.801-1.465 1.348-2.846 1.624l-.803.16V20h1c2.783 0 4.906-.771 6.309-2.292z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <blockquote class="mt-7">
                        <p class="text-lg text-black">“Excelentes profesionales, el trato fue exquisito. La atención fue rápida y eficaz. La clínica está muy bonita, luminosa y limpia. Recomendable 100%.”</p>
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="text-base font-semibold tex-tblack mt-9">Francisco</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="overflow-hidden bg-white rounded-md shadow">
                <div class="px-8 py-12">
                    <div class="relative w-24 h-24 mx-auto">
                        <Image class="relative object-cover w-24 h-24 mx-auto rounded-full" src={placeholder} alt="" />
                        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-600 rounded-full w-7 h-7">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                                <path
                                    d="M20.309 17.708C22.196 15.66 22.006 13.03 22 13V5a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-6c-1.103 0-2 .897-2 2v7a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h3.078a2.89 2.89 0 0 1-.429 1.396c-.508.801-1.465 1.348-2.846 1.624l-.803.16V20h1c2.783 0 4.906-.771 6.309-2.292zm-11.007 0C11.19 15.66 10.999 13.03 10.993 13V5a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-6c-1.103 0-2 .897-2 2v7a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h3.078a2.89 2.89 0 0 1-.429 1.396c-.508.801-1.465 1.348-2.846 1.624l-.803.16V20h1c2.783 0 4.906-.771 6.309-2.292z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <blockquote class="mt-7">
                        <p class="text-lg text-black">“Trato cercano, profesional y honesto. Clínica dental de total y absoluta confianza. Gracias por vuestro buen hacer!”</p>
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="text-base font-semibold tex-tblack mt-9">Jose Carlos</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="overflow-hidden bg-white rounded-md shadow">
                <div class="px-8 py-12">
                    <div class="relative w-24 h-24 mx-auto">
                        <Image class="relative object-cover w-24 h-24 mx-auto rounded-full" src={placeholder} alt="" />
                        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-600 rounded-full w-7 h-7">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                                <path
                                    d="M20.309 17.708C22.196 15.66 22.006 13.03 22 13V5a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-6c-1.103 0-2 .897-2 2v7a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h3.078a2.89 2.89 0 0 1-.429 1.396c-.508.801-1.465 1.348-2.846 1.624l-.803.16V20h1c2.783 0 4.906-.771 6.309-2.292zm-11.007 0C11.19 15.66 10.999 13.03 10.993 13V5a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-6c-1.103 0-2 .897-2 2v7a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h3.078a2.89 2.89 0 0 1-.429 1.396c-.508.801-1.465 1.348-2.846 1.624l-.803.16V20h1c2.783 0 4.906-.771 6.309-2.292z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <blockquote class="mt-7">
                        <p class="text-lg text-black">“Muy buena atención son unos profesionales hacen un trabajo de calidad y precio muy bueno son los mejores como dentistas y como personas.”</p>
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="text-base font-semibold tex-tblack mt-9">Jose Vicente</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
